notes.title: Author Contributions
notes.p: R.O. obtained the samples. R.O. and R.C. performed the chemical analysis. R.O., R.C., J.M., R.V., K.M. and M.Q. performed tests with the 3T3-cells. R.O. and Rony Lucas performed the antioxidante tests. R.O., L.F., L.O., and H.R. analyzed the data. R.O., R.L. and H.R. wrote the paper. L.F., L.O. and H.R. revised the paper.
